data.description: Step onto the allure of this meticulously updated 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom, fenced rambler in Tacoma, where modern comfort meets timeless charm. The heart of the home lies in it's stylish kitchen featuring granite countertops, custom cabinets, and stainless steel appliances, complemented by a separate utility/laundry room. Revel in the fresh ambiance of the newly painted interior, accentuated by wall-to-wall carpets in all 4 bedrooms, ensuring a cozy retreat. Entertain with ease on the outdoor patio, enhanced by a new cement slab in the spacious backyard. Conveniently located on a quiet street that is only minutes away from bus lines, Tacoma Mall, shopping, restaurants, parks, schools, and easily accessible to I-5.
